# {{ project_name }}

An A2A (Agent-to-Agent) Protocol compatible agent.

## Features

- **A2A Protocol**: Automatically exposes A2A endpoints
- **Agent Card**: Discoverable via `/.well-known/agent-card.json`
- **Streaming**: Full SSE streaming support

## A2A Endpoints

Once running, your agent is accessible at:

- Agent Card: `GET /a2a/{{ graph_name }}/.well-known/agent-card.json`
- Send Message: `POST /a2a/{{ graph_name }}/messages`
- Task Status: `GET /a2a/{{ graph_name }}/tasks/{task_id}`

## Integration

Other A2A agents can discover and call this agent using the standard protocol.

